Uses of Class
pkgMain.Screen

  • Uses of Screen in pkgMain

    Subclasses of Screen in pkgMain
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  AddPlantListScreen
    The PlantListScreen class is a screen that lists the plants in the garden.
    class  CreateNewGardenScreen
    The CreateNewGardenScreen represent the screen where the user can edit and create a garden.
    class  EditorScreen
    The EditorScreen class is a screen where the user can edit parts of the garden.
    class  EditPreexistingGardenScreen
    The EditPreexisitingGardenScreen displays a screen on which plants can be dragged onto the garden
    class  GenInfoScreen
    The GenInfoScreen shows some general information about why native plants are important in gardens
    class  LepListScreen
    The LepListScreen class is a screen that lists the leps in the garden.
    class  LoadGardenScreen
    The LoadGardenScreen allows the user to load a previously saved garden.
    class  MainScreen
    MainScreen displays the scene that shows the garden and allows the user to see many aspects of the garden, as well as access many different screens.
    class  PlantListScreen
    The screen that is responsible for displaying all the plants in a tableview.
    class  PlantMoreInfoScreen
    The screen that is responsible for displaying the informations for a plant.
    class  StartScreen
